  "description": "<h3>Back of Case - Nintendo DS (AUS) (from <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/crazy-pig/adblurbs\">Ad Blurbs</a>)</h3><h3>Take back the farm and Hog all the fun!</h3>\n<b>Meet Crazy Pig!</b> This fearless farmyard freedom fighter has decided to gain some revenge on the crafty wolf that's been hanging around the sty - and this is one ham-fisted pork product that plays dirty! Crazy Pig needs your help to clean up the farm and drive that nasty wolf away!<br><br>(screenshot captions)\n<ul>\n<li>Cry Wolf! Make your own piggy noises to drive bad things away, including those nasty buzzy bees!</li>\n<li>Bringing home the bacon! Plenty of piggy accessories to take care of me here, but more mud than soap please!</li>\n<li>Olym-pig games! Seasonal events keep me occupied all year long!</li>\n</ul>",
